Magnet fishing
Main Skill: Fishing
Max Efficiency: 230%

Pulling stuff out of a water body with a strong magnet rarely pays the bills, but helps a couple of good causes: it cleans the environment and it helps solve crimes. Be mindful of the regulations around it and have fun! You could pull anything!

The Magnet fishing activity is a Fishing activity.

Location

This activity can be done at the following location:

  • Old Arena Ruins in Grand Duchy of Trellin-Erdwise

Requirements

Skill Level Requirements:

  • At least Fishing lvl. 40.
  • At least Foraging lvl. 30.

Keyword Requirements:

  • Have Magnetic equipped.

Visibility

This activity is always visible.

Trivia

  • Normally Copper, gold and silver are generally non-magnetic Arenum magnets are just built different.
  • Prior to the Trinketry update the Heron trinket was a "Ring of the heron" and the only way to complete the My Precious achievement. The old rings were added to make up for the fact that the trinket no longer qualifies for that achievement.
